  "description": "Evolving atmosphere built around the Emergent layer. Creature calls are the foreground: Synth type (5) gives user control of formant position via creaturePitch. Canopy→Emergent formant route means the canopy spectral position shapes the creature voice in real time. Emergent→Canopy shimmer route means every call adds shimmer. A feedback ecology: call triggers shimmer; shimmer shapes the next call's formants.",
